 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',

 v0.departure_time, '"'||v5.days_code||'"', '"'||v6.day_name||'"',
 v6.year, v6.month_number, v6.day_number FROM flight v0,
